definitions.definition: An object that orbits another, especially a spacecraft that orbits a planet etc. without landing on it.
A person who constantly hangs around with someone they are attracted to, but too shy to talk to.

main_definition: An object that orbits another, especially a spacecraft that orbits a planet etc. without landing on it.
